" data-image-caption="&lt;p>;ホロアース 新エリア「オルタナティブ・シティv1」5月16日にオープン&lt;/p>;
" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/holoearth-new-area-alternative-city-v1-opens-on-may-16-2024.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/holoearth-new-area-alternative-city-v1-opens-on-may-16-2024.jpg" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/holoearth-new-area-alternative-city-v1-opens-on-may-16-2024.jpg" alt="Holo Earth新区“另类城市v1”5月16日开放" class="wp-image-125353"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>您将能够使用“ALTERMODE”来购买虚拟人物服装和配饰，以及“ALT BEAUTYS”来改变虚拟人物的体型、外观、发型等。</p><p> “另类城市”将继续添加各种设施和功能，作为“全息地球”的文化中心。</p><p></p><h4 id="outline__1_0_1" class="wp-block-heading">时装店“ALTERMODE” </h4><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczNbfK6_fAd6InD8dNGUfG0M6nDKkP7xI5P1glGMV0_zqeFjf5B9t7XivN_7tg1wSWeK8uT8XnhNY-RNQ0HWqZ8B8Vy3ZNQnxNaINYREA7s1C6O-vafmF4YRxjN7RsFWOHjtp0qaN-NF3aPTo66PNuVX=w1097-h307-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>时装店“ALTERMODE”在主街开业。您可以试穿和购买头像物品，例如衣服和配饰。</p><p></p><h3 id="outline__1_1" class="wp-block-heading">头像项目</h3><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczOG4gA9UUCJyvjo3FeUPwYCu4dmw5Mv-ncocEamYPhe0g7OHC5-NDOEb4tvy9x35b6-PE5rKY6nVZqLOPbYXjw9RlQaiQcFMm7IWCsbuhmyzFDu2HwHDC8MmW8cykAw9Ox6FXUYAvm2yZxN669Q-aGO=w1097-h617-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>第一批产品阵容共有 72 种头像物品。享受搭配适合外出的自己的衣服。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczNhWZ4XwfFs7we-NkCaBYogklKN2Z2EsIuOfJ6x-dJ3PcufrgVOkdLRwU4nEH4NSNiRGGGAL0W47FVXzUfKgtiQGdPDv3unB2qiSX72VAENcP8vD0llP12CBiF5nlQgkc-40YpKd-mq-JDEuuojDC1c=w1097-h307-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p></p><h4 id="outline__1_1_1" class="wp-block-heading">头像定制设施“ALT BEAUTYS” </h4><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczPua2yMDBlcUInfDxmDnIX5fVlpRFzaeFIg7EW3qgY6mwK1C9Gy09hNV5q1KR-mzuwJg4d9Y4pjTEnXsQoFb5K21rrfFs9x4g7by1MYu7L8J6-moeDw4LFJQl2SeRpkvtm_vVTTUoKC0o9IRtPR5cuA=w1097-h307-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p></p><p> “ALT BEAUTYS”将在中央大楼后面开业。</p><p> “ALT BEAUTYS”是一家设有时尚沙龙和诊所的设施。请在自定义或重建您的头像时使用它。</p><p> *要在此设施中自定义您的头像，您将需要“改变美丽点”和“重建核心”，这将在Ver0.7.0中添加。</p><p></p><h3 id="outline__1_2" class="wp-block-heading">风格沙龙</h3><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczPD2ALzNrr3hSlg8Y_zu3vDXTn0XGWmD3C9ESAb66diqs7U_YmAW4maXLtHMLXSTVgAQGazhVAOhmvyXoChkCyUSmXNhRdr8NhxfkPx-1Fd6TTEXMqvIqPsL4OMCXJQnekhRv6AfQqjaEvAOg3y0qzq=w1097-h617-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>在造型沙龙“ALT STYLE”中，您可以使用改变美丽点来定制您头像的脸部，包括眼睛、妆容和发型。</p><p>此外，作为该设施独有的功能，您可以为每个部位（正面/侧面/背面）定制发型。 </p><p></p><div class="uhssz6644dc8deb0d2" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
