</style><p>同日，Cover宣布准备将其股票上市从目前的东京证券交易所成长市场过渡到<strong>主要市场</strong>。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Gu0v2pi3eh"><a href="https://p2y.jp/cover-to-move-to-the-tse-prime-market-operates-hololive-production-etc/">封面 迁往东京证券交易所主要市场，运营 Hololive Productions 等</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“封面：进军东京证券交易所主要市场，运营 Hololive Productions 等 — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/cover-to-move-to-the-tse-prime-market-operates-hololive-production-etc/embed/#?secret=tvBdLSC7Ks#?secret=Gu0v2pi3eh" data-secret="Gu0v2pi3eh" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow"><p><a href="https://cover-corp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">封面有限公司</a></p><cite>官方网站</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“Mr.2”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber信息）</p><p></p><p></p><a href="https://p2y.jp/cover-corporation-4q-fy2024-financial-results/">与截至 2024 年 3 月的财年相比，《邮报》封面的销售额和利润大幅增长，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2Y.jp</a>上。]>;</content:encoded><wfw:commentrss> https://p2y.jp/cover-corporation-4Q-fy2024-financial-results/feed/</wfw:commentrss><slash:comments> 0</slash:comments><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 125278</post-id></item><item><title>涵盖 TSE 运营至 Prime Market、Holive Productions 等。</title><link/> https://p2y.jp/cover-to-move-to-to-the-prime-prime-Market-Operates-hololive-product-etc/<comments> https://p2y.jp/cover-to-move-to-to-the-prime-prime-Market-Operates-hololive-product-etc/#respondond</comments><dc:creator><![CDATA[p2y_admin Mon, 13 May 2024 09:17:22 +0000 VTuberバーチャルメタバースカバー株式会社東京証券取引所 https://p2y.jp/?p=125259 <p>运营 VTuber Office Holo Live Productions 的 Cover Co., Ltd. 准备于 2024 年 5 月 13 日将股票上市